### ========================================
### VARIABLES
### ========================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@orgId = org-123
@courseId = course-123
@classId = class-456
@userId = user-456
@studentId = student-789
@groupId = group-123
@lessonNodeId = lesson-123
@moduleId = module-123
@homeworkId = homework-123
@classLessonNodeId = classLessonNode-123

# Test user credentials
@testEmail = testuser@example.com
@testPassword = Test@123456
@testName = Test User


### ========================================
### AUTHENTICATION (RUN THESE FIRST!)
### ========================================

### 1. Sign Up (tạo user mới)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/sign-up/email
Content-Type: application/json
Origin: http://localhost:3000

{
  "email": "{{testEmail}}",
  "password": "{{testPassword}}",
  "name": "{{testName}}"
}

### 2. Sign In (đăng nhập để lấy session)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/sign-in/email
Content-Type: application/json
Origin: http://localhost:3000

{
  "email": "{{testEmail}}",
  "password": "{{testPassword}}"
}

### 3. Get Current Session (kiểm tra session hiện tại)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/session
Origin: http://localhost:3000


### ========================================
### HEALTH CHECK
### ========================================

### Check API health
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health


### ========================================
### USERS
### ========================================

### Search user by email
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/search?email=user@example.com

### Search user by email (with valid user)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/search?email=tranductamhoctap@gmail.com


### ========================================
### PERMISSIONS
### ========================================

### Check if current user is admin
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/permissions/is-admin


### ========================================
### COURSES
### ========================================

### Get all courses in an organization
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/courses?organizationId={{orgId}}

### Get course by slug
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/courses/by-slug/my-org/intro-course

### Create a new course
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/courses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Introduction to Web Development",
  "slug": "intro-web-dev",
  "organizationId": "{{orgId}}",
  "description": "Learn the basics of web development"
}

### Add a lesson node to course
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/courses/{{courseId}}/nodes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "parentId": "root",
  "type": "module",
  "title": "Module 1: Fundamentals",
  "content": {
    "description": "Introduction to fundamentals"
  }
}

### Add a lesson under module
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/courses/{{courseId}}/nodes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "parentId": "{{moduleId}}",
  "type": "lesson",
  "title": "Lesson 1: HTML Basics",
  "content": {
    "description": "Learn HTML basics"
  }
}

### Add homework node
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/courses/{{courseId}}/nodes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "parentId": "{{lessonNodeId}}",
  "type": "homework",
  "title": "Homework 1: Build a Simple Page",
  "content": {
    "description": "Create your first webpage"
  }
}

### Update a lesson node
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/courses/{{courseId}}/nodes/node-123
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Lesson Title",
  "content": {
    "description": "Updated description"
  }
}

### Reorder/move a lesson node
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/courses/{{courseId}}/nodes/node-123/reorder
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "targetParentId": "module-456",
  "targetIndex": 0
}

### Delete a lesson node
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/courses/{{courseId}}/nodes/node-123

### Get homework status for course
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/courses/homework-status?courseId={{courseId}}&classId={{classId}}


### ========================================
### CLASSES
### ========================================

### Get current user's classes
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/classes

### Get specific class with course data
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/classes/class-123

### Create a new class
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/classes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Web Dev - Class A",
  "courseId": "{{courseId}}",
  "organizationId": "{{orgId}}"
}

### Add a member to class
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/classes/class-123/members
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "{{userId}}",
  "role": "teacher"
}

### Add student to class
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/classes/class-123/members
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "{{studentId}}",
  "role": "student"
}

### Get all students in a class
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/classes/class-123/students

### Get student's pending assignments
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/classes/class-123/pending-assignments

### Get pending assignments for multiple classes (batch)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/classes/pending-assignments-batch
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "classIds": ["class-123", "class-456", "class-789"]
}


### ========================================
### CLASS GROUPS
### ========================================

### Create a class group
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/class-groups
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "classId": "class-123",
  "name": "Group A - Beginners",
  "description": "Students new to programming"
}

### Update a class group
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/class-groups/{{groupId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "classId": "class-123",
  "name": "Group A - Updated Name",
  "description": "Updated description"
}

### Add member to class group
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/class-groups/{{groupId}}/members
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "classId": "class-123",
  "userId": "{{studentId}}"
}

### Remove member from class group
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/class-groups/{{groupId}}/members/{{studentId}}?classId=class-123

### Delete a class group
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/class-groups/{{groupId}}?classId=class-123


### ========================================
### CLASS LESSON NODES
### ========================================

### Load class lesson nodes for a lesson
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/class-lesson-nodes?lessonNodeId={{lessonNodeId}}&classId={{classId}}

### Get counts of class lesson nodes
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/class-lesson-nodes/counts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "lessonNodeIds": ["lesson-123", "lesson-456"],
  "classId": "{{classId}}"
}

### Create a class lesson node (lesson note)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/class-lesson-nodes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "lessonNodeId": "{{lessonNodeId}}",
  "classId": "{{classId}}",
  "type": "lesson_note",
  "content": {
    "notes": "Important points from the lesson",
    "timestamp": "2024-01-15T10:30:00Z"
  }
}

### Create a class lesson node (homework implementation)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/class-lesson-nodes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "lessonNodeId": "{{homeworkId}}",
  "classId": "{{classId}}",
  "type": "homework_imp",
  "content": {
    "submissionId": "submit-789",
    "code": "console.log('Hello World');",
    "status": "submitted"
  }
}

### Delete a class lesson node
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/class-lesson-nodes/{{classLessonNodeId}}?classId={{classId}}

### Get build run ID from lesson node
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/class-lesson-nodes/{{lessonNodeId}}/build-run

### Get assignment stats for a class
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/class-lesson-nodes/assignment-stats/{{classId}}


### ========================================
### MEMBERS
### ========================================

### Check if user belongs to organization
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/members/check?orgId={{orgId}}

### Check if user belongs to organization by slug
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/members/check?orgSlug=my-org

### Add a member to an organization
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/members
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "organizationId": "{{orgId}}",
  "userId": "{{userId}}",
  "role": "admin"
}

### Add member to organization as member role
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/members
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "organizationId": "{{orgId}}",
  "userId": "user-789",
  "role": "member"
}


### ========================================
### WIDGETS
### ========================================

### Get all widgets
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/widgets


### ========================================
### HƯỚNG DẪN SỬ DỤNG / USAGE GUIDE
### ========================================
###
### 🔐 AUTHENTICATION (Phải chạy trước tiên!)
### ───────────────────────────────────────
### 1. Chạy "Sign Up" để tạo user mới (lần đầu)
###    - Hoặc "Sign In" nếu user đã tồn tại
### 2. Response sẽ trả về session → REST Client tự lưu cookie
### 3. Sau đó các request khác sẽ tự động có session
###
### ✅ SỰ CỐ GIẢI QUYẾT UNAUTHORIZED
### ───────────────────────────────────────
### - Endpoint yêu cầu authentication: phải chạy Sign In trước
### - @AllowAnonymous() endpoints: không cần session
###   * /api/health (check server status)
###   * /api/widgets (get all widgets)
###
### 🔄 COOKIE BEHAVIOR
### ───────────────────────────────────────
### - REST Client tự động lưu & gửi cookie từ Sign In response
### - Cookie được lưu và dùng cho tất cả request tiếp theo
### - Nếu cookie hết hạn/bị xóa → phải Sign In lại
###
### 📝 CHỈNH SỬA VARIABLES
### ───────────────────────────────────────
### - Thay đổi @testEmail, @testPassword tại phần VARIABLES
### - Hoặc click "Edit Request" trên từng request để customize
### - Các @orgId, @courseId, v.v. dùng giá trị test - thay bằng ID thực tế từ DB
###
### 🚀 NEXT STEPS
### ───────────────────────────────────────
### 1. Click "Send Request" trên "Sign Up" → tạo user
### 2. Nếu error (user tồn tại) → run "Sign In" thay vì Sign Up
### 3. Check response từ Sign In → xem session info
### 4. Bây giờ có thể test các endpoint khác
### 5. Cập nhật @orgId, @courseId, @classId bằng ID thực tế để test với data
###